      "id": "PopularPost363066",
      "post_content": "Excellent by today's standards, Lightning Bolt was even better in the day's of Revised. It saw play in an environment that didn't shy away from burn. [Fireball](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireball), [Disintegrate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disintegrate), [Earthquake](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Earthquake), and [Chain Lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chain Lightning) all helped make \"3 to your face\" even more deadly. Lightning Bolt also saw a lot of action taking out your opponent's mid-sized creatures. [Juggernaut](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Juggernaut)s, [Phantom Monster](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phantom Monster)s, [Hypnotic Specter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hypnotic Specter)s, [Kird Ape](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kird Ape)s, and all manner of knights and bears met their untimely ends thanks to this card.",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost363066\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Excellent by today's standards, Lightning Bolt was even better in the day's of Revised.  It saw play in an environment that didn't shy away from burn.  <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireball\">Fireball</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disintegrate\">Disintegrate</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Earthquake\">Earthquake</a>, and <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chain Lightning\">Chain Lightning</a> all helped make \"3 to your face\" even more deadly.  Lightning Bolt also saw a lot of action taking out your opponent's mid-sized creatures.  <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Juggernaut\">Juggernaut</a>s, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phantom Monster\">Phantom Monster</a>s, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hypnotic Specter\">Hypnotic Specter</a>s, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kird Ape\">Kird Ape</a>s, and all manner of knights and bears met their untimely ends thanks to this card.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                  